'''Roo-wood''' was a form of [[Wood/Legends|wood]] used to make furniture. The [[Rhysode Room]] in the [[Jedi Academy (Ossus)|Jedi Academy]] on [[Ossus/Legends|Ossus]] had a serenity table constructed with it. [[Blue Star]] [[Casino/Legends|casino]] on [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Valnoos/Legends|Valnoos]] also had expensive roo-wood chairs.

